{"tid":1375784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香城Online:鐵匠做盾","createTime":"2019-07-28T06:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T18:39:36.000Z","uid":96551,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18271cc06ae66195ada2117be7984c34dfa54717","tid":1375784,"uid":96551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:51:54.000Z","msg":"代人Post,朋友打機做鐵匠，而且好中意焗蛋糕。<br />\n尋日打機時係元朗共和國行街見到好多玩家冇盾，有頭盔有豬咀又如何？被怪打點算？<br />\n<br />\n鐵匠同大家分享一下做盾心得。<br />\n<br />\n上海街一向都係鐵匠買裝備既地方，做蛋糕當然要有洞焗爐盤。<br />\n特色：<br />\n1)可擋棍<br />\n2)可檔彈<br />\n3)可擋刀<br />\n4)輕身<br />\n5)有洞，可以係有保護時又可以睇到前面<br />\n6)可以即場組合， 用索帶加毛巾就已經好舒服<br />\n7)唔怕比怪周，中意焗蛋糕都唔得？<br />\n8)平，65至85蚊有交易<br />\n<br />\n上海街 x榮 用現金比仲有9折， 多款選擇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcvVVdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcvVVdk.png&h=8f02f15c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就唔post我鐵匠個盾啦，以免D怪認得，各位繼續升Level, 武運亨昌<br />\n<br />\nSorry post 錯台"},{"pid":"81c6f948ff368a0c9b5101d99b0aed2daae2fc45","tid":1375784,"uid":175316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"咁簿真係擋到彈嗎?"},{"pid":"828e76727e91dec7e00faba611d75e7d44acaf60","tid":1375784,"uid":175316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c483a1b7b5c31c86f9b9c79751577192c8c1e7e","tid":1375784,"uid":83558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d99e508bf14efd6f4e18ed3fbbed71696d2fe16e","tid":1375784,"uid":165808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:22:17.000Z","msg":"上環蘇杭街應該都有大量"},{"pid":"5dcd5ef22c7526b981fd9cecbd36cdf0a00cf64a","tid":1375784,"uid":78300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:35:46.000Z","msg":"太薄喎<br />\n早2日鋼板都射穿<br />\n要再諗諗"},{"pid":"afef5d62eaf0f8d597070d8d7fd05b237b01e215","tid":1375784,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18: